            "heading": "Our Approach",
            "sub_title_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "a7dab157-b607-401b-b61d-2976f78d0bbe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Christy, we know that everything we make has an impact and we're developing systems to reduce ours. We're striving to create dreamy nights' sleeps and relaxing bath routines that are gentler on our planet. Since 1850, we've had an uncompromising design philosophy; creating functional, beautiful products that are made to last. In recent years, it's become clear that we need to go farther than that—so we can all rest a little easier.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
