        "title": "<p>We’re just getting started</p>",
        "billboard_title_font_size_mob": 16,
        "billboard_title_font_size_desktop": 40,
        "billboard_title_font_weight": "400",
        "billboard_title_font_family": "Hatton, serif",
        "copy": "<p>From transitioning to Better Cotton, to introducing our first certified organic collection, we're continuously learning and improving so that we can make products that are better for you and better for the planet. You're invited to learn more about our current certifications, goals, how we're developing, and what we're moving towards.</p>",
