    "images-copy-cta": {
      "type": "images-copy-cta",
      "blocks": {
        "e1fa53b6-c495-4a81-aba7-f9493869f9f0": {
          "type": "subtitle",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "But what does better mean?"
          }
        },
        "aca3113c-97cb-48bd-ad31-1a56263404aa": {
          "type": "copy",
          "settings": {
            "copy": "<p>A few things, really. The Better Cotton  trains farmers in practices that actively promote soil health, water stewardship, carbon capture, and biodiversity. </p>"
          }
        },
        "87ccc695-1c4d-4ea9-afe9-32ff4781f1f6": {
          "type": "subtitle",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "Their 2030 strategy maps out five impact targets:-"
          }
        },
        "c5b1210b-7ac1-4264-8168-37f59a5afd19": {
          "type": "copy",
          "settings": {
            "copy": "<p>Increasing the net income and resilience of two million   smallholder cotton farmers and workers- Empower women working in cotton through educational   training and resources- Ensure that 100% of Better Cotton Farmers have improved    the health of their soil- Reduce the use and risk of synthetic pesticides applied by    BCI farmers by at least half. - Reduce greenhouse gas emissions by 50% per tonne of    Better Cotton lint.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
